      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1997 Acura NSX-T is a masterclass in mid-engine dynamics, featuring the high-revving C32B 3.2L V6 with VTEC engagement that remains razor-sharp. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal corner exit. This example boasts a pristine all-aluminum monocoque chassis with zero oxidation and original factory welds. The double-wishbone suspension retains its factory compliance, and the four-channel ABS system has been meticulously maintained. With perfect compression across all cylinders and a leak-free cooling system, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
