      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that redefines the 'mint' standard. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a mirror-like finish with zero paint chips, dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by original overlays since day one, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a fully documented history of preventative maintenance with every service stamp performed on schedule at the dealership. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in fresh rubber, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
